markdownreadercopy-pref-help = Remi is the local bridge between Zotero and your MCP workflow. It watches a local queue folder and executes safe write actions inside Zotero. 中文说明：Remi 是 Zotero 与 MCP 工作流之间的本地桥接器，会监听本地队列文件，并在 Zotero 内执行安全写入操作。
